flowchart TD
    Start([Game Start]) --> PlayerChoice{Player Chooses}

    PlayerChoice -->|Rock| ClickRock[Play Click Sound]
    PlayerChoice -->|Paper| ClickPaper[Play Click Sound]
    PlayerChoice -->|Scissors| ClickScissors[Play Click Sound]

    ClickRock & ClickPaper & ClickScissors --> ClearLogs[Clear Logs if First Move]
    ClearLogs --> GenRandom[Generate Random Number]
    GenRandom --> UmairDecide{Determine Umair Move}

    UmairDecide -->|0-0.33| UmairRock[Umair: Rock]
    UmairDecide -->|0.33-0.67| UmairPaper[Umair: Paper]
    UmairDecide -->|0.67-1| UmairScissors[Umair: Scissors]

    UmairRock --> UpdateLogs[Update Move Logs]
    UmairPaper --> UpdateLogs
    UmairScissors --> UpdateLogs

    UpdateLogs --> CompareChoices{Compare Choices}
    CompareChoices -->|Same| Tie[Result: Try Again]
    CompareChoices -->|Umair Beats Player| UmairWins[Result: Umair Wins]
    CompareChoices -->|Player Beats Umair| PlayerWins[Result: You Win]

    Tie --> UpdateScore1[Update Score Display]
    UmairWins --> UpdateScore2[Umair Score +1]
    PlayerWins --> UpdateScore3[You Score +1]

    UpdateScore1 --> DisplayResult[Display Result]
    UpdateScore2 --> DisplayResult
    UpdateScore3 --> DisplayResult

    DisplayResult --> GameContinue{Reset Button Clicked?}
    GameContinue -->|Yes| PlayResetSound[Play Reset Sound]
    GameContinue -->|No| PlayerChoice
    PlayResetSound --> ResetGame[Reset Scores & Logs]
    ResetGame --> Start